---
// About.astro
---

<section id="about" class="h-[80vh] flex items-center bg-zinc-950 py-8">
  <div class="container px-6 mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
    <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
      <div class="relative w-92 h-92">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-purple-500 blur-xl opacity-50 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="relative w-full h-full rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-purple-500">
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl font-bold">
            <img src="Paisaje.webp" alt="Paisaje bonito" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl ml-8 font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-500">
        About me
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-3 text-xl px-8">
        Hi, I'm Samuel, a Computer Engineering student with a strong interest in web development. 
        I'm passionate about creating engaging projects and learning new technologies to constantly improve my skills. 
        My goal is to become a full-stack developer, specializing in building dynamic, efficient, and scalable web experiences.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-3 text-xl px-8">
        Outside of coding, soccer is one of my biggest passions, I love playing and following my favorite teams. 
        I also enjoy video games, especially titles like Counter-Strike, Fortnite, and FC25. When it comes to music, I usually go for rap.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


  
  
